<paragraph id="2E15F27FFF97FFAD38E0A7F6FAB3FC88" blockId="7.[151,1437,151,861]" box="[199,1381,764,789]" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">
<emphasis id="1CDE2E6DFF97FFAD38E0A7F6FE91FC89" bold="true" box="[199,327,764,789]" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Etymology</emphasis>
. The word 
<taxonomicName id="E9AA89FCFF97FFAD39E0A7F6FDEFFC88" box="[455,569,764,788]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Merodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="408" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="adriaticus">
<emphasis id="1CDE2E6DFF97FFAD39E0A7F6FDEFFC88" box="[455,569,764,788]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">adriaticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
refers to the known range of the species, restricted to the Adriatic coast.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2E15F27FFF97FFAD38E0A615FE95FCC1" blockId="7.[151,1437,151,861]" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">
<emphasis id="1CDE2E6DFF97FFAD38E0A615FDF5FCA4" bold="true" box="[199,547,799,824]" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Range and preferred habitat.</emphasis>
Adriatic coast (
<figureCitation id="B691EEFAFF97FFAD3AF2A615FCC0FCA4" box="[725,790,799,824]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[151,252,1981,2003]" captionTargetBox="[161,1426,1308,1960]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[161,1426,1308,1960]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Distribution of Merodon adriaticus sp. n. (●) and Merodon rufipes (▲)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/556011/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
); Mediterranean scrub, evergreen Adriatic thermophilous 
<taxonomicName id="E9AA89FCFF97FFAD38B0A64EFF23FCC7" box="[151,245,836,859]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="7" pageNumber="408" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="1CDE2E6DFF97FFAD38B0A64EFF23FCC7" box="[151,245,836,859]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="408">Quercus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
forest.
</paragraph>
